name: Make America Based Again
description: About MABA Let's get real - Trump isn't just another pup in the pack. He's the alpha, leading the world pack with more sass than a cat on a hot tin roof. Why? Because we're riding high on the Base Blockchain, the kind of tech so spicy, it had tech moguls sliding into our DMs for a peek. We told them, Back off, big brains! This tech is too hot to handle!
